      <div class="msgContentFrame">&lt;Sparkle Magic&gt; is one of the most active guilds on the server per member. Even if we don't have the gigantic numbers of Taint or AIE, we make up for it with Achievementwhorism, PvP junkies, and very, very active raiders. Many folks raid with multiple toons. <br /> <br />You're always welcome Pigtails =) There are benefits to being in a huge guild, but there are benefits to a smaller one too. Personally, there are rare times when I miss being in the Taint, but right now I wouldn't give up my SM peeps to go back. <br /> <br /> <br /><span class="sm">Yes, it was intentional. =P</span> <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Oct  7th 2010  3:45pm by TherionSaysWhat </span></i><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><span class="sm">&quot;I'm gonna need to see more math I don't understand to believe all this&quot; <br /> <br /><a href="HTTP://www.wowarmory.com/character-sheet.xml?r=Proudmoore&amp;n=Zede" rel="external nofollow" title="www.wowarmory.com/character-sheet.xml?r=Proudmoore&amp;n=Zede">Zede the Undying</a>  <a href="HTTP://www.wowarmory.com/character-sheet.xml?r=Proudmoore&amp;n=Phezz" rel="external nofollow" title="www.wowarmory.com/character-sheet.xml?r=Proudmoore&amp;n=Phezz">Phezz, the Insane Kingslayer</a>  <a href="HTTP://www.wowarmory.com/character-sheet.xml?r=Proudmoore&amp;n=Dehlia" rel="external nofollow" title="www.wowarmory.com/character-sheet.xml?r=Proudmoore&amp;n=Dehlia">Dehlia the Love Fool</a></span></div></div>
